But the first, I have thought of it for a while.

555
00:35:11,319 --> 00:35:16,079
Could you be more girlish in the future?

556
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:20,960
You mean...

557
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:23,038
I lack femininity?

558
00:35:23,039 --> 00:35:24,038
No, no.

559
00:35:24,039 --> 00:35:25,239
How could it be? I...

560
00:35:26,759 --> 00:35:27,960
I am worried about you.

561
00:35:28,640 --> 00:35:31,119
I am worried that you always fight regardless of your own life,

562
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:33,278
and plan it effortlessly.

563
00:35:33,279 --> 00:35:34,079
Little counsellor,

564
00:35:35,079 --> 00:35:35,999
give me a chance,

565
00:35:36,839 --> 00:35:38,200
and let me be your man.

566
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:40,360
I will protect you in the future.

567
00:35:42,519 --> 00:35:45,640
But I know you are like a wild horse.

568
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,399
You have your own world.

569
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:48,359
I respect you.

570
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:50,478
I would never stop you from anything you want to do.

571
00:35:50,479 --> 00:35:52,440
But no matter in what situation,

572
00:35:53,279 --> 00:35:54,920
you can't risk your life,

573
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:57,359
nor can you leave without telling me.

574
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:59,120
No matter what happens, we will face it together.

575
00:36:00,160 --> 00:36:03,079
No matter if it's wind or storm, or swords or arrows,

576
00:36:04,239 --> 00:36:05,799
Me, Ashile Sun would fend against it.

577
00:36:07,759 --> 00:36:08,680
Clear?

578
00:36:10,839 --> 00:36:11,759
This...

579
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:14,400
I'll go and see.

580
00:36:25,799 --> 00:36:26,599
Sun!

581
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:28,400
Sun!

582
00:36:32,640 --> 00:36:33,838
Sun!

583
00:36:33,839 --> 00:36:35,038
Sun!

584
00:36:35,039 --> 00:36:36,639
Sun! Don't scare me!

585
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:37,879
Sun!

586
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:39,119
Help!

587
00:36:39,120 --> 00:36:40,160
Please! Help!

588
00:36:40,799 --> 00:36:42,159
Sun!

589
00:36:42,160 --> 00:36:43,279
Sun!

590
00:37:30,640 --> 00:37:31,440
Who are you?

591
00:37:34,559 --> 00:37:38,400
Eagle Division and Bear Division are completely annihilated.

592
00:38:06,039 --> 00:38:08,039
Why are they dismantling tents?

593
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:10,079
Are they going to remove?

594
00:38:13,279 --> 00:38:14,839
What happened?

595
00:38:19,079 --> 00:38:20,399
Two main forces!

596
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:21,960
How could they be annihilated?

597
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,679
Ashile Sun! What is he planning?

598
00:38:25,680 --> 00:38:28,519
What can a dead man plan?

599
00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:32,519
Sun is dead,

600
00:38:33,319 --> 00:38:34,920
I have no reason to live.

601
00:38:36,120 --> 00:38:39,720
You can kill me whenever you want.

602
00:38:45,239 --> 00:38:46,880
Sun is the god of war on grasslands.

603
00:38:48,279 --> 00:38:49,640
No one can kill him!

604
00:38:50,519 --> 00:38:51,880
What can valiancy do?

605
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:54,120
He can't escape from a back stab!

606
00:38:54,839 --> 00:38:58,759
So many people here want him to die!

607
00:38:59,519 --> 00:39:00,640
Even so,

608
00:39:01,559 --> 00:39:04,200
Sun asked me to go back with his last breath,

609
00:39:04,799 --> 00:39:08,999
