616
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:52,360
What a pity for what happened on Eagle and Bear Division!

617
00:39:53,519 --> 00:39:57,278
I'm afraid if Khan can't accept his son's death,

618
00:39:57,279 --> 00:39:59,239
his situation would become worse.

619
00:40:00,120 --> 00:40:03,798
So after he is better, I will tell him about it.

620
00:40:03,799 --> 00:40:05,279
Great Khan is ill?

621
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:08,360
For a few days.

622
00:40:09,079 --> 00:40:12,998
Now he even can't talk.

623
00:40:12,999 --> 00:40:13,999
What disease?

624
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:17,318
I don't know what he is suffering from.

625
00:40:17,319 --> 00:40:19,479
Grand Witches are helping him effortlessly.

626
00:40:20,039 --> 00:40:20,999
What a pity!

627
00:40:22,160 --> 00:40:25,360
I haven't told Tegin Sun about it,

628
00:40:26,519 --> 00:40:30,799
