631
00:40:42,600 --> 00:40:43,720
Don't be afraid.

632
00:40:44,479 --> 00:40:46,359
If there's really a secret in it,

633
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:50,400
Great Khan will be on Tegin Sun and Eagle Division's side.

634
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:54,079
Khatun.

635
00:40:55,200 --> 00:40:56,680
There is a traitor in Eagle Division.

636
00:40:57,239 --> 00:40:59,440
All the people are dead because of her.

637
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,599
I am to blame.

