641
00:41:07,600 --> 00:41:08,720
Who is she?

642
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:10,440
I have no idea.

643
00:41:11,680 --> 00:41:14,999
When I decided to ask her, she killed herself with her sword.

644
00:41:16,999 --> 00:41:20,759
Till now, no one knows who sent her there.

645
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:25,559
I'll tell this to the women and children of Eagle Division.

646
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,999
